<div id="directCont"><label class="locAndDirectLbl">Directions</label>
<p id="directionInstruc"> From South Super Highway take Sta. Rosa exit then turn right. Go straight all the way to Tagaytay Market via Silang, Cavite then turn right at the junction (note that if you turn left, you are heading to the Picnic Groove). Heading Tagaytay Rotonda turn left again enroute way to Taal Vista or Batangas, just go straight. You will be passing by Josephine's Restaurant, Robinson's Summit Ridge, Taal vista, Mercury Drug (right side), Mendez Crossing, Jolibee, and Sotogrande. After Sotogrande, turn right to Mayor Maglabe Drive (note that Villa Fely's Garden has the same street going to Hacienda Isabella and Paradizoo). Go straight until you see a hardware named "Bili Dito", then turn right on next street. You will then see a chapel on your left side. Go straight then left again on the next street (landmark: on your left is a basketball court). Straight to the end of concrete road then left.
</p>
</div>
